            <h1>How to use PRISA</h1>
            <b>Workflow:</b>
            <div class="d-flex p-2">
                <ol>
                    <li>Click on 'Upload' menu option, you will be redirected to the Upload page 
                        (Note: PRISA only accepts .avi or .jpg file formats).</li>
                    <li>Once on the Upload page, you will see a progress bar and a field to submit a file(s).</li>
                    <li>To choose a file(s), click the button labelled, "Choose Files."</li>
                    <li>There will be a File Explorer pop up in your browser, allowing you to search your computer
                        for appropriate upload files.
                    </li>
                    <li>To select multiple files, hold down the "command" key while clicking.</li>
                    <li>When finished, click "open" in your file browser with the appropriate file(s) selected.</li>
                    <li>Your file names should appear to the right of the "Choose Files" button.</li>
                    <li>When you are ready to submit for upload, click the "Submit" button.</li>
                    <li>The progress bar will inform you of the upload progress.</li>
                    <li>Appropriate errors will pop up if there were problems during the upload.</li>
                    <li>Within 20 seconds per person, per frame, the top possible 3 matches in the PRISA database
                        will appear on screen.
                    </li>     
                </ol>
